channel.title: When ever I tele somewhere, it doesn't tele
channel.description:
Hello, when ever I tele somewhere on my server, It will just say Loading -- Please Wait. Then if I disconnect sever it will show where I was suppose to go, then disconnect me. Then when I log back in, i'm back to where I teled from.
Thanks!
